 You were, I believe, teaching at naturopathic colleges after you'd gotten your PhD.

00:16:47.560 --> 00:16:51.960
 And you, I think where we left off in the last show, you had decided to start recommending

00:16:51.960 --> 00:16:56.880
 progesterone use to some of your nutritional patients.

