 You worked as a nutritional consultant, I think, also.

00:17:00.960 --> 00:17:02.780
 Yeah.

00:17:02.780 --> 00:17:12.100
 I guess I was teaching endocrinology at the naturopath school, but I was doing mostly

00:17:12.100 --> 00:17:16.420
 nutritional counseling at home.

00:17:16.420 --> 00:17:26.740
 And I found that it was more and more involved hormone interactions with the foods.

