 The doctors at first would tell the patients not to come back because they had personality

00:19:39.460 --> 00:19:44.020
 defects that they wouldn't accept their advice.

00:19:44.020 --> 00:19:45.020
 Like I said, very open-minded.

00:19:45.020 --> 00:19:46.020
 Yeah.

